704671f-a.text:
Graham Ave., between Maujer (left) and Stagg (right) Streets, as seen across clearing looking north,- east from Scholes Street and Manhattan Ave., showing at the left, St. John's Evang. Lutheran Church, on the north side of Maujer Street, between Graham Ave., and Humboldt Street, and in the background, St. Catherine's Hospital on the east side of Bushwick Ave., between Maujer and Ten Eyck Streets.

October 27, 1936.
L. Sperr.
